quam elit ante, malesuada id, tempor eu, gravida id, odio. Maecenas suscipit, risus et eleifend imperdiet, nisi orci ullamcorper massa, et adipiscing orci velit quis magna.</figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\">\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><p>-This third column has a quote</p><cite>Theme Reviewer<br></cite></blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>But wait there is more!</strong>&nbsp; We also have a block called <em>Media &amp; Text,</em> which is a two column block that helps you display media and text content next to each other, without having to first setup a column block:</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text alignwide\"><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><span class=\"wp-image-617 inline-gatsby-image-wrapper gatsby-image-wrapper\" style=\"position:relative;overflow:hidden;max-width:100%;width:640px\" data-reactroot=\"\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width:100%;padding-bottom:75%\"></span><img aria-hidden=\"true\" src=\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\" alt=\"\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:0;transition-delay:500ms\"/><picture><source srcSet=\"/nx-gastby-blogs/static/cfd9e551880a229bddb00b5b1943f5a4/f7be0/dsc20050813_115856_52.jpg 160w,\n/nx-gastby-blogs/static/cfd9e551880a229bddb00b5b1943f5a4/b4845/dsc20050813_115856_52.jpg 320w,\n/nx-gastby-blogs/static/cfd9e551880a229bddb00b5b1943f5a4/bbe0c/dsc20050813_115856_52.jpg 640w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\"/><img sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" srcSet=\"/nx-gastby-blogs/static/cfd9e551880a229bddb00b5b1943f5a4/f7be0/dsc20050813_115856_52.jpg 160w,\n/nx-gastby-blogs/static/cfd9e551880a229bddb00b5b1943f5a4/b4845/dsc20050813_115856_52.jpg 320w,\n/nx-gastby-blogs/static/cfd9e551880a229bddb00b5b1943f5a4/bbe0c/dsc20050813_115856_52.jpg 640w\" src=\"/nx-gastby-blogs/static/cfd9e551880a229bddb00b5b1943f5a4/bbe0c/dsc20050813_115856_52.jpg\" alt=\"dsc20050813_115856_52\" loading=\"eager\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:1;transition:opacity 500ms\"/></picture><noscript><picture><source srcset=\"/nx-gastby-blogs/static/cfd9e551880a229bddb00b5b1943f5a4/f7be0/dsc20050813_115856_52.jpg 160w,\n/nx-gastby-blogs/static/cfd9e551880a229bddb00b5b1943f5a4/b4845/dsc20050813_115856_52.jpg 320w,\n/nx-gastby-blogs/static/cfd9e551880a229bddb00b5b1943f5a4/bbe0c/dsc20050813_115856_52.jpg 640w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" /><img loading=\"eager\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" srcset=\"/nx-gastby-blogs/static/cfd9e551880a229bddb00b5b1943f5a4/f7be0/dsc20050813_115856_52.jpg 160w,\n/nx-gastby-blogs/static/cfd9e551880a229bddb00b5b1943f5a4/b4845/dsc20050813_115856_52.jpg 320w,\n/nx-gastby-blogs/static/cfd9e551880a229bddb00b5b1943f5a4/bbe0c/dsc20050813_115856_52.jpg 640w\" src=\"/nx-gastby-blogs/static/cfd9e551880a229bddb00b5b1943f5a4/bbe0c/dsc20050813_115856_52.jpg\" alt=\"dsc20050813_115856_52\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;opacity:1;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center\"/></picture></noscript></span></figure><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\">\n<p class=\"has-large-font-size\">Media &amp; Text</p>\n\n\n\n<p>A paragraph block sits ready to be used, below your headline.</p>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n</div></div>\n","title":"Block: Columns","date":"November 02, 2018","featuredImage":null},"previous":{"author":{"node":{"firstName":"Tyler","lastName":"Barnes","name":"tylbar","uri":"/author/tyler/","avatar":{"url":"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/0a5bd2d18281009a03f01b8378abada1?s=96&d=mm&r=g"}}},"id":"cG9zdDoxNzUy","excerpt":"<p>Gallery blocks have two settings: the number of columns, and whether or not images should be cropped. The default number of columns is three, and the maximum number of columns is eight. Below is a three column gallery at full width, with cropped images. Some more text for taking up space. A two column gallery, [&hellip;]</p>\n","date":"November 03, 2018","title":"Block: Gallery","uri":"/block-gallery/","featuredImage":{"node":{"altText":"Boat Barco Texture","localFile":{"url":"https://wpgatsbydemo.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2008/06/img_8399.jpg"}}}},"next":{"author":{"node":{"firstName":"Tyler","lastName":"Barnes","name":"tylbar","uri":"/author/tyler/","avatar":{"url":"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/0a5bd2d18281009a03f01b8378abada1?s=96&d=mm&r=g"}}},"id":"cG9zdDoxNzQ5","excerpt":"<p>The quote block has two styles,&nbsp;regular: Gutenberg is more than an editor. The Gutenberg Team and large: Yes, it is a press, certainly, but a press from which shall flow in inexhaustible streams, the most abundant and most marvelous liquor that has ever flowed to relieve the thirst of men! Johannes Gutenberg The quote blocks [&hellip;]</p>\n","date":"November 01, 2018","title":"Block: Quote","uri":"/block-quotes/","featuredImage":null}},"pageContext":{"id":"cG9zdDoxNzQz","previousPostId":"cG9zdDoxNzUy","nextPostId":"cG9zdDoxNzQ5"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3159585216"]}